608333144.text: "To determine whether mesonephric cells positive for KDR-LacZ were affected by VEGFA signal transduction inhibition, E11 KDR-LacZ mouse testis organ cultures were treated with VEGFR-TKI, a VEGFA receptor tyrosine kinase antagonist, which inhibits both KDR and FLT1."
